{
  "meta": { "is_partial": true, "description": "옵션 선택, 선택상품 목록, 구매 버튼 카드" },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale'}}",
  "props": { "className": "bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5" },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "=== 배송 불가 사전 경고 (B8 — 선택 배송국가로 배송 불가) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-start gap-2 px-3 py-2.5 mb-4 rounded-lg border bg-red-50 border-red-200 dark:bg-red-900/20 dark:border-red-800" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": { "name": "triangle-exclamation", "size": "sm", "className": "text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium text-red-700 dark:text-red-300" },
          "text": "$t:shop.shippability.not_shippable"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 옵션 선택 안내 텍스트 (2개 이상 옵션 있고, 아직 선택 안 했을 때만, 판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale' && product.data?.has_options && product.data?.option_groups?.length > 0 && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 && (!_local.selectedOptionItems || _local.selectedOptionItems.length === 0)}}",
      "props": { "className": "border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-4 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-sm font-medium mb-4" },
      "text": "$t:shop.product.select_options_guide"
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 옵션 선택 섹션 (옵션 그룹이 있고 선택할 옵션이 2개 이상일 때만, 판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "id": "option-select",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale' && product.data?.has_options && product.data?.option_groups?.length > 0 && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1}}",
      "props": { "className": "mb-4 space-y-3" },
      "children": [
        {
          "comment": "옵션 그룹별 Select",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "iteration": { "source": "{{product.data?.option_groups ?? []}}", "item_var": "group", "index_var": "groupIndex" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": { "className": "mb-3" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Label",
                  "props": { "className": "block text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" },
                  "text": "{{group.name_localized}}"
                },
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Select",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "option_{{groupIndex}}",
                    "className": "w-full",
                    "value": "{{_local.currentSelection?.[group.name_localized] ?? ''}}",
                    "placeholder": "{{groupIndex === 0 || _local.currentSelection?.[product.data?.option_groups[groupIndex - 1]?.name_localized] ? group.name_localized + '$t:shop.product.select_option_suffix' : '$t:shop.product.select_upper_option_first'}}",
                    "disabled": "{{groupIndex > 0 && !_local.currentSelection?.[product.data?.option_groups[groupIndex - 1]?.name_localized]}}",
                    "options": "{{[{ value: '', label: groupIndex === 0 || _local.currentSelection?.[product.data?.option_groups[groupIndex - 1]?.name_localized] ? group.name_localized + $t('shop.product.select_option_suffix') : $t('shop.product.select_upper_option_first') }, ...($computed.optionChoices?.[groupIndex] ?? (group.values_localized ?? []).map(v => ({ value: v, label: v })))] ?? []}}"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "change",
                      "handler": "sequence",
                      "actions": [
                        {
                          "comment": "현재 선택 상태 업데이트",
                          "handler": "setState",
                          "params": {
                            "target": "local",
                            "currentSelection": "{{Object.assign({}, _local.currentSelection ?? {}, { [group.name_localized]: $event.target.value })}}"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "comment": "마지막 옵션 선택 시 자동으로 selectedOptionItems에 추가 (newGroupName/newValue로 sequence 상태 동기화 우회)",
                          "handler": "sirsoft-basic.addSelectedItemIfComplete",
                          "params": {
                            "productId": "{{product.data?.id}}",
                            "optionGroups": "{{product.data?.option_groups}}",
                            "options": "{{product.data?.options}}",
                            "currentSelection": "{{_local.currentSelection ?? {}}}",
                            "selectedOptionItems": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []}}",
                            "preferredCurrency": "{{_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW'}}",
                            "additionalOptionGroups": "{{product.data?.additional_options ?? []}}",
                            "newGroupName": "{{group.name_localized}}",
                            "newValue": "{{$event.target.value}}"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 수량 선택만 표시 (옵션 없거나, 기본 옵션 1개뿐인 상품, 판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale' && (!product.data?.has_options || !product.data?.option_groups || product.data?.option_groups.length === 0 || (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) <= 1)}}",
      "props": { "className": "mb-4" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" },
              "text": "$t:shop.product.quantity"
            },
            {
              "type": "composite",
              "name": "QuantitySelector",
              "props": {
                "value": "{{_local.noOptionQuantity ?? 1}}",
                "min": "{{product.data?.min_purchase_qty ?? 1}}",
                "max": "{{product.data?.max_purchase_qty > 0 ? Math.min(product.data.max_purchase_qty, product.data?.stock_quantity ?? 999) : (product.data?.stock_quantity ?? 999)}}",
                "size": "sm"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "event": "onChange",
                  "handler": "sirsoft-basic.updateNoOptionQuantity",
                  "params": {
                    "newQuantity": "{{$args[0]}}",
                    "multiCurrencyUnitPrice": "{{product.data?.multi_currency_selling_price}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 수량 제한 안내 (판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale' && (product.data?.min_purchase_qty > 1 || product.data?.max_purchase_qty > 0)}}",
      "props": { "className": "px-1 mb-2 space-y-0.5" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "if": "{{product.data?.min_purchase_qty > 1}}",
          "props": { "className": "block text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
          "text": "$t:shop.min_purchase_qty_notice|qty={{product.data?.min_purchase_qty}}"
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "if": "{{product.data?.max_purchase_qty > 0}}",
          "props": { "className": "block text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
          "text": "$t:shop.max_purchase_qty_notice|qty={{product.data?.max_purchase_qty}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 선택한 상품 섹션 (옵션 있는 상품, 총 금액 위에 표시, 판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale' && product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 && _local.selectedOptionItems && _local.selectedOptionItems.length > 0}}",
      "props": { "className": "border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4 mb-4" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "H4",
          "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3" },
          "text": "$t:shop.selected_products"
        },
        {
          "comment": "선택된 상품 목록 (space-y-4 는 부모, iteration 은 자식 — 분리해야 형제 간 간격 적용됨)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "space-y-4" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "iteration": { "source": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []}}", "item_var": "item", "index_var": "itemIndex" },
              "props": { "className": "bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700/50 rounded-lg p-3" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "상품 옵션명 + 삭제 버튼",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between mb-2" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
                      "text": "{{item.options ? Object.values(item.options).join(' / ') : ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Button",
                      "props": { "className": "text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 dark:hover:text-gray-200 cursor-pointer" },
                      "children": [
                        { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "x", "size": "sm" } }
                      ],
                      "actions": [
                        {
                          "type": "click",
                          "handler": "sirsoft-basic.removeSelectedItem",
                          "params": {
                            "itemIndex": "{{itemIndex}}",
                            "selectedOptionItems": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems}}"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "=== 블럭별 추가옵션 그룹 선택 (D2/D10: 옵션 블럭 내부) ===",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "if": "{{product.data?.additional_options?.length > 0}}",
                  "props": { "className": "mb-3 space-y-2" },
                  "iteration": { "source": "{{product.data?.additional_options ?? []}}", "item_var": "addGroup", "index_var": "addGroupIndex" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Div",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Label",
                          "props": { "className": "block text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1" },
                          "children": [
                            { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "{{addGroup.name}}" },
                            {
                              "type": "basic",
                              "name": "Span",
                              "if": "{{addGroup.is_required}}",
                              "props": { "className": "text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 ml-0.5" },
                              "text": "*"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "composite",
                          "name": "Select",
                          "props": {
                            "name": "add_option_{{itemIndex}}_{{addGroup.id}}",
                            "className": "w-full",
                            "value": "{{item.additionalOptionSelections?.[addGroup.id] ?? ''}}",
                            "placeholder": "$t:shop.additional_option_placeholder",
                            "options": "{{[{ value: '', label: $t('shop.additional_option_placeholder') }, ...(addGroup.values ?? []).map(v => ({ value: v.id, label: v.price_adjustment > 0 ? v.name + ' (' + (v.price_adjustment_formatted ?? ('+' + v.price_adjustment.toLocaleString())) + ')' : v.name }))]}}"
                          },
                          "actions": [
                            {
                              "type": "change",
                              "handler": "sirsoft-basic.setBlockAdditionalOption",
                              "params": {
                                "itemIndex": "{{itemIndex}}",
                                "additionalOptionId": "{{addGroup.id}}",
                                "valueId": "{{$event.target.value}}",
                                "selectedOptionItems": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems}}",
                                "additionalOptionGroups": "{{product.data?.additional_options ?? []}}",
                                "preferredCurrency": "{{_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW'}}"
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "comment": "직접입력 칸 — 선택된 선택지가 allow_custom_text 일 때만 노출(입력 필수). 입력란임이 명확하도록 라벨 + 테두리/배경 스타일 적용",
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Div",
                          "if": "{{(addGroup.values ?? []).find(v => v.id === item.additionalOptionSelections?.[addGroup.id])?.allow_custom_text === true}}",
                          "props": { "className": "mt-2" },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "basic",
                              "name": "Label",
                              "props": { "className": "block text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1" },
                              "text": "$t:shop.additional_option_custom_text_label"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "basic",
                              "name": "Input",
                              "props": {
                                "type": "text",
                                "name": "add_option_text_{{itemIndex}}_{{addGroup.id}}",
                                "className": "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500",
                                "value": "{{item.additionalOptionCustomTexts?.[addGroup.id] ?? ''}}",
                                "placeholder": "$t:shop.additional_option_custom_text_placeholder",
                                "maxLength": 255
                              },
                              "actions": [
                                {
                                  "type": "input",
                                  "handler": "sirsoft-basic.setBlockAdditionalOption",
                                  "params": {
                                    "itemIndex": "{{itemIndex}}",
                                    "additionalOptionId": "{{addGroup.id}}",
                                    "valueId": "{{item.additionalOptionSelections?.[addGroup.id]}}",
                                    "customText": "{{$event.target.value}}",
                                    "selectedOptionItems": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems}}",
                                    "additionalOptionGroups": "{{product.data?.additional_options ?? []}}",
                                    "preferredCurrency": "{{_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW'}}"
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "추가옵션 추가금 합계 표기 (선택된 추가금이 있을 때)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "if": "{{(item.additionalOptionsTotal ?? 0) > 0}}",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2" },
                  "children": [
                    { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:shop.additional_options_amount" },
                    { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "{{(() => { const c = (_global.availableCurrencies ?? []).find(x => x.is_default); const dp = c?.decimal_places ?? 0; const n = (item.additionalOptionsTotal ?? 0).toLocaleString(undefined, { minimumFractionDigits: dp, maximumFractionDigits: dp }); const s = c?.symbol ?? '₩'; return '+' + ((c?.code === 'KRW' || s === '₩' || s === '원') ? (n + '원') : (s + n)); })()}}" }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "수량 조절 + 가격",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "QuantitySelector",
                      "props": {
                        "value": "{{item.quantity}}",
                        "min": 1,
                        "max": "{{item.stock}}",
                        "size": "sm"
                      },
                      "actions": [
                        {
                          "event": "onChange",
                          "handler": "sirsoft-basic.updateSelectedItemQuantity",
                          "params": {
                            "itemIndex": "{{itemIndex}}",
                            "newQuantity": "{{$args[0]}}",
                            "selectedOptionItems": "{{_local.selectedOptionItems}}",
                            "preferredCurrency": "{{_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW'}}"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": { "className": "text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
                      "text": "{{item.multiCurrencyTotalPrice?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? item.totalPriceFormatted}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "=== 총 금액 + 구매 버튼 섹션 (판매중일 때만) ===",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.sales_status === 'on_sale'}}",
      "props": { "className": "border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4" },
      "children": [
        {
          "comment": "총 금액 (옵션 선택형 상품 - 2개 이상)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex justify-between items-center mb-4" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:shop.total_amount ({{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.quantity, 0)}}$t:shop.count_unit)"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).length === 0 ? '-' : (_local.selectedTotalMultiCurrency?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? _local.selectedOptionItems[0]?.multiCurrencyTotalPrice?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? _local.selectedOptionItems[0]?.totalPriceFormatted ?? '')}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "총 금액 (옵션 없거나 기본 옵션 1개뿐인 상품)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!product.data?.has_options || (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) <= 1}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex justify-between items-center mb-4" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:shop.product.total_amount ({{_local.noOptionQuantity ?? 1}}$t:shop.product.count_unit)"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{_local.noOptionTotalMultiCurrency?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? product.data?.multi_currency_selling_price?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? product.data?.selling_price_formatted ?? ''}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "=== 바로구매 + 장바구니 버튼 (PC 2단, 모바일 1단) ===",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2" },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "바로구매 버튼",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "className": "w-full py-3 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                "disabled": "{{_local.isOrdering || product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-center gap-2" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "if": "{{_local.isOrdering}}",
                      "props": { "name": "spinner", "spin": true, "size": "md" }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{!_local.isOrdering}}",
                      "text": "$t:shop.product.buy_now"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{_local.isOrdering}}",
                      "text": "$t:shop.product.ordering"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "conditions",
                  "conditions": [
                    {
                      "comment": "배송 불가 차단 (B8 클라 가드 — 선택 배송국가로 배송 불가, 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.shippability.not_shippable" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "if": "{{product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 && (!_local.selectedOptionItems || _local.selectedOptionItems.length === 0)}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.product.please_select_options" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "필수 추가옵션 미선택 차단 (D9/D12 클라 가드 — 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).some(item => (product.data?.additional_options ?? []).filter(g => g.is_required).some(g => !item.additionalOptionSelections?.[g.id]))}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.additional_option_required" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "직접입력 허용 선택지 선택 시 텍스트 미입력 차단 (Q-E1 클라 가드 — 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).some(item => (product.data?.additional_options ?? []).some(g => { const sel = item.additionalOptionSelections?.[g.id]; const v = (g.values ?? []).find(x => x.id === sel); return g.is_required && v?.allow_custom_text === true && (item.additionalOptionCustomTexts?.[g.id] ?? '').trim() === ''; }))}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.additional_option_custom_text_required" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "then": {
                        "handler": "sequence",
                        "actions": [
                          { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "local", "isOrdering": true } },
                          {
                            "comment": "바로 구매: 장바구니 미경유 — direct_items 로 바로 체크아웃(장바구니 오염 없음)",
                            "handler": "apiCall",
                            "auth_mode": "optional",
                            "target": "/api/modules/sirsoft-ecommerce/checkout",
                            "params": {
                              "method": "POST",
                              "headers": { "X-Cart-Key": "{{_global.cartKey}}" },
                              "body": "{{product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 ? { direct_items: (_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).map(item => ({ product_id: product.data?.id, option_values: item.optionValues, quantity: item.quantity, additional_option_selections: Object.entries(item.additionalOptionSelections ?? {}).filter(([, vid]) => vid != null).map(([gid, vid]) => ({ additional_option_id: Number(gid), value_id: Number(vid), custom_text: item.additionalOptionCustomTexts?.[Number(gid)] })) })) } : { direct_items: [{ product_id: product.data?.id, quantity: _local.noOptionQuantity ?? 1 }] }}}"
                            },
                            "onSuccess": [
                              {
                                "comment": "로그인: 주문서로 직행 / 비로그인: 로그인 페이지(비회원 주문 선택) 경유. 임시주문은 cart_key(localStorage)로 유지되어 복귀 후에도 조회됨",
                                "handler": "conditions",
                                "conditions": [
                                  {
                                    "if": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid}}",
                                    "then": { "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/checkout" } }
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "then": {
                                      "handler": "navigate",
                                      "params": {
                                        "path": "/login",
                                        "query": { "redirect": "{{_global.shopBase}}/checkout" }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            ],
                            "onError": [
                              { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "local", "isOrdering": false } },
                              { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "error", "message": "{{error.errors?.message ?? error.message}}" } }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "장바구니 버튼",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "className": "w-full py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                "disabled": "{{_local.isAddingToCart || _local.isOrdering || product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}"
              },
              "children": [
                { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "if": "{{!_local.isAddingToCart}}", "props": { "name": "shopping-cart", "size": "lg" } },
                { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "if": "{{_local.isAddingToCart}}", "props": { "name": "spinner", "size": "lg", "className": "animate-spin" } },
                { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:shop.product.add_to_cart" }
              ],
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "conditions",
                  "conditions": [
                    {
                      "comment": "배송 불가 차단 (B8 클라 가드 — 선택 배송국가로 배송 불가, 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.shippability.not_shippable" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "if": "{{product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 && (!_local.selectedOptionItems || _local.selectedOptionItems.length === 0)}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.product.please_select_options" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "필수 추가옵션 미선택 차단 (D9/D12 클라 가드 — 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).some(item => (product.data?.additional_options ?? []).filter(g => g.is_required).some(g => !item.additionalOptionSelections?.[g.id]))}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.additional_option_required" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "직접입력 허용 선택지 선택 시 텍스트 미입력 차단 (Q-E1 클라 가드 — 서버도 422 재검증)",
                      "if": "{{(_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).some(item => (product.data?.additional_options ?? []).some(g => { const sel = item.additionalOptionSelections?.[g.id]; const v = (g.values ?? []).find(x => x.id === sel); return g.is_required && v?.allow_custom_text === true && (item.additionalOptionCustomTexts?.[g.id] ?? '').trim() === ''; }))}}",
                      "then": { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "warning", "message": "$t:shop.additional_option_custom_text_required" } }
                    },
                    {
                      "then": {
                        "handler": "sequence",
                        "actions": [
                          { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "local", "isAddingToCart": true } },
                          {
                            "handler": "apiCall",
                            "auth_mode": "optional",
                            "target": "/api/modules/sirsoft-ecommerce/cart",
                            "params": {
                              "method": "POST",
                              "headers": { "X-Cart-Key": "{{_global.cartKey}}" },
                              "body": "{{product.data?.has_options && (product.data?.options?.length ?? 0) > 1 ? { product_id: product.data?.id, items: (_local.selectedOptionItems ?? []).map(item => ({ option_values: item.optionValues, quantity: item.quantity, additional_option_selections: Object.entries(item.additionalOptionSelections ?? {}).filter(([, vid]) => vid != null).map(([gid, vid]) => ({ additional_option_id: Number(gid), value_id: Number(vid), custom_text: item.additionalOptionCustomTexts?.[Number(gid)] })) })) } : { product_id: product.data?.id, items: [{ quantity: _local.noOptionQuantity ?? 1 }] }}}"
                            },
                            "onSuccess": [
                              { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "local", "isAddingToCart": false, "selectedOptionItems": [], "currentSelection": {}, "noOptionQuantity": 1, "additionalOptions": {} } },
                              { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "global", "cartCount": "{{response.data.cart_count}}" } },
                              { "handler": "openModal", "target": "cart_added_modal" }
                            ],
                            "onError": [
                              { "handler": "setState", "params": { "target": "local", "isAddingToCart": false } },
                              { "handler": "toast", "params": { "type": "error", "message": "{{error.errors?.message ?? error.message}}" } }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
